### Implementation

```java
// DiscordVoiceBot.java
public class DiscordVoiceBot extends ListenerAdapter {
    private PlayerPositionManager posManager;
    private ProximityVoiceManager proxManager;
    
    @Override
    public void onSlashCommandInteraction(SlashCommandInteractionEvent event) {
        if (event.getName().equals("position")) {
            double x = event.getOption("x").getAsDouble();
            double y = event.getOption("y").getAsDouble();
            double z = event.getOption("z").getAsDouble();
            
            UUID userId = UUID.fromString(event.getUser().getId());
            posManager.updatePosition(userId, x, y, z, "discord");
            
            event.reply("Position updated!").queue();
            
            // Update voice channels based on proximity
            updateVoiceChannels(event.getGuild());
        }
    }
    
    private void updateVoiceChannels(Guild guild) {
        // Get all users and their positions
        Map<UUID, Set<UUID>> proximityGroups = calculateProximityGroups();
        
        // Move users to appropriate voice channels
        for (Map.Entry<UUID, Set<UUID>> entry : proximityGroups.entrySet()) {
            // Create or use existing voice channel for this group
            VoiceChannel channel = getOrCreateProximityChannel(guild, entry.getKey());
            
            // Move all nearby users to this channel
            for (UUID nearbyUser : entry.getValue()) {
                Member member = guild.getMemberById(nearbyUser.toString());
                if (member != null) {
                    guild.moveVoiceMember(member, channel).queue();
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
```

### Discord Commands

```
/position x:10 y:5 z:20    - Set your position
/proximity range:50        - Set proximity range
/voicemode whisper         - Set voice mode
/nearby                    - Show nearby players
```

### KullanÄ±m

1. **Bot'u Discord'a ekle**
2. **KomutlarÄ± kullan:**
   ```
   /position x:0 y:0 z:0
   ```
3. **Voice channel'a gir**
4. **Bot otomatik olarak proximity'e gÃ¶re channel deÄŸiÅŸtirir**

